android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN.description: Allows an application to configure the local Bluetooth phone and to discover and pair with remote devices.

android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

playstore_details.title: BOSS Revolution® - Cheap International Calling
playstore_details.description:
Stay in touch with friends and family around the world with the new and improved BOSS Revolution App. Make cheap and crystal-clear international calls with the most innovative technology.

Here’s what you’ll get with BOSS Revolution’s International Call App:

Improved call quality and low international rates.
• Make crystal-clear phone calls anytime and anywhere with Boss Revolution.  
• Save up to 90% on your international calls vs. what mobile carrier may charge
• Enjoy high quality and cheap calls to more than 200 countries including Guatemala, Nigeria, Dominican Republic, Honduras, Colombia, El Salvador, Mexico, Ecuador, Peru, Cuba, Ghana, Jamaica, Kenya, Haiti, Ethiopia and many more!
• Free calls to other BOSS Revolution app users around the world when you both use your data or Wi-Fi connection (with app version 4.0 or higher)

Easily top up the prepaid mobile phones of your friends and family in 90+ countries with more than 150 carriers. (available in selected markets)
• Popular mobile carriers to reload include: Tigo, Claro, Cubacel, MTN, Orange, Airtel, Natcom, Flow, Digicel, Glo
• See the latest international carrier promotions right in the app. 

Upgraded and faster messaging experience with NEW status markers.
• Message and share content with any BOSS Revolution app user for FREE (with app version 4.0 or higher)
• Chat one-on-one or in groups
• Share pictures, stickers, videos, voice messages and more

With BOSS Revolution you can feel closer to home. Try the app today and see why millions of people worldwide love using BOSS Revolution.

Plus, U.S. consumers get $1 FREE to try the BOSS Revolution calling service. Just activate the app by 12/31/2020.

BOSS Revolution is committed to handling user data securely. To view our User Data Policy, go to: https://www.bossrevolution.com/app/user-privacy-en-US.html
